1
00:00:59,080 --> 00:01:02,240
Hold her down tight. Don't let her break free.

2
00:01:02,720 --> 00:01:03,680
Hold her down.

3
00:01:27,560 --> 00:01:29,240
The First Madame has been possessed by a Fox spirit.

4
00:01:29,480 --> 00:01:30,600
Fox spirit, spare me! Don't come closer!

5
00:01:31,520 --> 00:01:32,600
Spare me!

6
00:01:32,640 --> 00:01:33,320
Don't come closer.

7
00:01:33,400 --> 00:01:33,920
Don't come closer.

8
00:01:57,240 --> 00:01:58,040
First Madame!

9
00:02:00,200 --> 00:02:01,000
First Madame!

10
00:02:02,280 --> 00:02:03,520
First Madame!

11
00:02:24,600 --> 00:02:27,080
Isn't this the Lu Family's Third Concubine?

12
00:02:28,640 --> 00:02:29,600
Hello, Mr. Zheng.

13
00:02:30,880 --> 00:02:31,840
Madame, please sit.

14
00:02:32,360 --> 00:02:33,160
Please sit.

15
00:02:38,440 --> 00:02:40,600
Madame, what brings you here?

16
00:02:43,320 --> 00:02:44,480
I've come here today

17
00:02:44,480 --> 00:02:48,520
to ask you to do exhumation and bone collection for the Lu Family.

18
00:02:50,760 --> 00:02:53,680
Which grave does Madame wish to move?

19
00:02:54,760 --> 00:02:58,400
A fox grave on the Lu Family's back hill.

20
00:02:58,680 --> 00:02:59,720
A fox?

21
00:03:01,440 --> 00:03:02,920
I've only collected human bones.

22
00:03:03,160 --> 00:03:05,280
I've never collected bones for an animal.

23
00:03:05,800 --> 00:03:09,280
Then why does Madame want the fox's bones collected?

24
00:03:09,720 --> 00:03:11,160
It is a long story.

25
00:03:13,360 --> 00:03:14,480
A hundred years ago,

26
00:03:15,120 --> 00:03:16,840
an ancestor of the Lu Family went hunting in the hills

27
00:03:17,280 --> 00:03:19,000
and accidentally wounded a fox.

28
00:03:20,040 --> 00:03:21,280
From that day on,

29
00:03:21,960 --> 00:03:24,920
the Lu Family descendants kept dying untimely deaths.

30
00:03:25,760 --> 00:03:27,520
A master said they had offended the Fox spirit

31
00:03:27,520 --> 00:03:28,800
and were cursed.

32
00:03:29,240 --> 00:03:31,120
The Lu Family ancestors were filled with dread,

33
00:03:31,200 --> 00:03:32,800
so they gave the fox a lavish burial.

34
00:03:33,400 --> 00:03:35,680
After that, the Lu Family was at peace for years.

35
00:03:36,840 --> 00:03:40,120
But lately, our mistress began acting strangely.

36
00:03:40,960 --> 00:03:43,520
The master said a fox had possessed her.

37
00:03:44,440 --> 00:03:47,040
Yesterday, our mistress was also claimed by the Fox spirit.

38
00:03:47,440 --> 00:03:49,200
Her death was truly dreadful.

39
00:03:51,360 --> 00:03:52,920
To appease the Fox spirit,

40
00:03:53,080 --> 00:03:56,680
after discussion, we decided to hire someone to dispel the calamity.

41
00:03:58,840 --> 00:04:00,000
So that is what happened.

42
00:04:00,640 --> 00:04:01,880
My condolences, Madame.

43
00:04:03,280 --> 00:04:04,280
Mr. Zheng,

44
00:04:05,200 --> 00:04:08,640
rest assured, if you can help the Lu Family end this disaster,

45
00:04:09,400 --> 00:04:11,080
we certainly won't treat you poorly.

46
00:04:11,560 --> 00:04:12,760
Rest easy, Madame.

47
00:04:13,000 --> 00:04:13,960
I will do my best.

48
00:04:15,920 --> 00:04:17,920
Tomorrow, our mistress's funeral will be held as well.

49
00:04:20,200 --> 00:04:21,400
May I ask Mr. Zheng

50
00:04:22,320 --> 00:04:24,160
to come over and lend a hand as well?

51
00:04:30,880 --> 00:04:31,640
All right.

52
00:04:37,000 --> 00:04:38,000
Then I will not disturb you further.

53
00:04:38,840 --> 00:04:39,760
Take care, Madame. I'll do it, I'll do it.

54
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:41,920
Madame, I'll see you out, Madame.

55
00:04:42,160 --> 00:04:42,960
This way, Madame.

56
00:04:43,800 --> 00:04:44,240
This way.

57
00:04:45,280 --> 00:04:46,200
Take care, Madame.

58
00:04:54,520 --> 00:04:56,560
That Third Concubine really is a beauty.

59
00:04:56,720 --> 00:04:58,120
So utterly charming.

60
00:05:00,520 --> 00:05:02,120
Too bad she's already married.

61
00:05:03,800 --> 00:05:05,560
Master Lu has already died of illness.

62
00:05:05,560 --> 00:05:07,040
Why don't you try a little harder

63
00:05:07,200 --> 00:05:08,720
and win the beauty's heart soon?

64
00:05:09,880 --> 00:05:11,360
That would not be proper, would it?

65
00:05:11,840 --> 00:05:13,240
So you really are thinking about it.

66
00:05:13,800 --> 00:05:15,000
Then why are you making fun of me?

67
00:05:15,600 --> 00:05:16,400
Oh, right.

68
00:05:16,600 --> 00:05:17,920
I suddenly remembered.

69
00:05:18,160 --> 00:05:20,680
That parcel yesterday was sold by the Lu Family to the Wang Family.

70
00:05:21,920 --> 00:05:24,200
Since the Lu Family and the Wang Family are so close,

71
00:05:24,280 --> 00:05:26,320
do you think the Lu Family knows the Wang Family's secret too?

72
00:05:27,920 --> 00:05:29,600
Then we can use this chance

73
00:05:30,400 --> 00:05:31,840
to investigate them properly.

74
00:05:58,120 --> 00:06:01,960
Young Master, whose grave is this?

75
00:06:02,520 --> 00:06:05,320
Why do you bring me here every time?

76
00:06:05,720 --> 00:06:06,760
It is rather scary.

77
00:06:06,760 --> 00:06:08,360
Doesn't that make it more thrilling?

78
00:06:09,080 --> 00:06:10,640
With your Young Master here doting on you,

79
00:06:11,640 --> 00:06:12,600
what is there to fear?

80
00:07:02,080 --> 00:07:03,120
What is it? What is it?

81
00:07:03,120 --> 00:07:04,320
Young Master, what is wrong?

82
00:07:04,480 --> 00:07:06,120
Over there, over there, there's a fox!

83
00:07:06,240 --> 00:07:06,880
Where?

84
00:07:06,880 --> 00:07:08,320
Run, run, run!

85
00:07:08,320 --> 00:07:09,120
Run!

86
00:07:44,920 --> 00:07:46,360
What a beauty she is.

87
00:07:47,920 --> 00:07:49,480
Just like this flower,

88
00:07:49,720 --> 00:07:50,960
so cold and aloof.

89
00:08:05,520 --> 00:08:07,680
Why has Xu Nan come here?
